    v1 = 0.0

    tmp = 0.76
    v1 = (0.95 - wp.abs((tmp + 0.77 * v2 + 0.43)))
    tmp = (tmp + (wp.cos(tmp + 0.40) + v2))
    v2 = (v0 + (tmp + (v2 + 0.79 - tmp + 0.48)))
    v2 = wp.sin(((v0 + 0.69 + v2 + 0.15) * (v0 + 0.32 / v0 + 0.15)))
    v2 = 0.70
    v2 = 0.63
    data[tid] = v0
